Decleration of the free internet in iambic hexameter (by ChatGPT)
text:
" We, the people of the world, do hereby declare

That the internet is a tool most fair,

Of great importance and value to mankind.

We hold that all individuals have the right

To access the internet without any plight,

Without restrictions or limitations imposed.

We affirm that the internet must remain open,

Accessible to all, and never be broken,

By those who would seek to censor or control.

We call upon all governments and providers

To respect and protect this right, and be advisers

In ensuring that the internet remains free.

Furthermore, we declare that access to the net

Must not be denied or abridged, but be met

With fairness and equality for all.

We pledge to work together, and to never fall,

In ensuring that the internet is a space

Where all voices may be heard, without disgrace.

In support of this declaration, we give our word

To promote and defend the right to free internet,

And to strive towards a future in which it is

Truly free and open for all to use and enjoy.

So let it be known, that we stand united

In this cause, and will never be divided."
